do not seem to pay it any mind.

279
00:26:59,826 --> 00:27:01,453
Did that upset you?

280
00:27:01,536 --> 00:27:03,705
Not at all. It is no big deal.

281
00:27:03,788 --> 00:27:05,790
They cannot hold government posts anyway.

282
00:27:05,874 --> 00:27:08,960
