they should not become a nuisance.

288
00:27:25,727 --> 00:27:26,770
Mother.

289
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:31,441
They are more thoughtful than you think.
You do not have to worry.

290
00:27:31,524 --> 00:27:35,236
They may be mischievous,
but they would never harm anyone.

291
00:27:37,280 --> 00:27:38,281
All right.

292
00:27:39,699 --> 00:27:44,037
