-Watch your mouth!

337
00:32:57,725 --> 00:33:00,853
One's criticisms only ring hollow
unless one earns their right.

338
00:33:00,937 --> 00:33:02,313
Be it your studies or character,

339
00:33:02,397 --> 00:33:05,108
