My legs are still numb after having
kneeled for so long yesterday.

436
00:42:35,970 --> 00:42:37,221
Stop it.

437
00:42:39,682 --> 00:42:40,641
Prince Simso!

438
00:42:41,225 --> 00:42:43,102
